<!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_f066b85ce1693dad" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_f066b85ce1693dad" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">To get a live link for your Instagram bio with as little effort as possible, the "Pro" way is to use <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="101">Vercel</b>. It’s free, it’s fast, and it will give you a clean link like <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="170">sujal-portfolio.vercel.app</code>.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Since you want "copy and paste" work, here is the fastest shortcut to do it without using a terminal:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="2">Step 1: Put your code on GitHub (The Easy Way)</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="3"><li><p data-path-to-node="3,0,0">Go to <response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c872387312="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c872387312="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c601438958="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_f066b85ce1693dad&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_528b7089c94038af&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]]" href="https://github.com/" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahcKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQNg">GitHub.com</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element> and create a free account.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,1,0">Click <b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="6">"New Repository"</b>. Name it <code data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="32">my-portfolio</code>. Keep it <b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="54">Public</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,2,0">Instead of using code commands, just click the link that says <b data-path-to-node="3,2,0" data-index-in-node="62">"uploading an existing file"</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,3,0">Drag and drop all the files and folders I gave you into the browser window.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,4,0">Scroll down and click <b data-path-to-node="3,4,0" data-index-in-node="22">"Commit changes"</b>.</p></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="4"><h3 data-path-to-node="5">Step 2: Get your Link via Vercel (The "One-Click" Step)</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="6"><li><p data-path-to-node="6,0,0">Go to <response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c872387312="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c872387312="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c601438958="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_f066b85ce1693dad&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_528b7089c94038af&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]]" href="https://vercel.com/" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahcKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQNw">Vercel.com</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element> and sign up using your <b data-path-to-node="6,0,0" data-index-in-node="40">GitHub account</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,1,0">Click the <b data-path-to-node="6,1,0" data-index-in-node="10">"Add New"</b> button and select <b data-path-to-node="6,1,0" data-index-in-node="38">"Project"</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,2,0">You will see your <code data-path-to-node="6,2,0" data-index-in-node="18">my-portfolio</code> repository listed there. Click <b data-path-to-node="6,2,0" data-index-in-node="62">"Import"</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,3,0">Vercel will automatically detect it’s a Vite/React project. Just click <b data-path-to-node="6,3,0" data-index-in-node="71">"Deploy"</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,4,0">Wait about 60 seconds. You’ll see a confetti animation!</p></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="7"><h3 data-path-to-node="8">Step 3: Put it in your Instagram Bio</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="9"><li><p data-path-to-node="9,0,0">Vercel will give you a link (e.g., <code data-path-to-node="9,0,0" data-index-in-node="35">https://my-portfolio-three.vercel.app</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Copy</b> that link.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,2,0">Open Instagram → <b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="17">Edit Profile</b> → <b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="32">Links</b> → <b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="40">Add External Link</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">Paste</b> your URL.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="10">"I want it even faster" (The Zero-Setup Method)</h3><p data-path-to-node="11">If you don't want to deal with GitHub yet, use <b data-path-to-node="11" data-index-in-node="47">StackBlitz</b>:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="12"><li><p data-path-to-node="12,0,0">Go to <response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c872387312="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c872387312="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c601438958="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_f066b85ce1693dad&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_528b7089c94038af&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]]" href="https://stackblitz.com/" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahcKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQOA">StackBlitz.com</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="12,1,0">Select <b data-path-to-node="12,1,0" data-index-in-node="7">"Vite"</b> (React).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="12,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="12,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Copy and paste</b> the code I gave you into the <code data-path-to-node="12,2,0" data-index-in-node="44">App.jsx</code> and <code data-path-to-node="12,2,0" data-index-in-node="56">index.css</code> files.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="12,3,0">Click the <b data-path-to-node="12,3,0" data-index-in-node="10">"Share"</b> button at the top right.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="12,4,0">Copy the <b data-path-to-node="12,4,0" data-index-in-node="9">"Editor URL"</b> or <b data-path-to-node="12,4,0" data-index-in-node="25">"App URL"</b>.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="13"><b data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="0">Wait, a quick heads-up:</b>
Since you are currently in 7th grade, having a "Master’s Degree in London" on your bio might confuse people who actually know you! If you want a version that reflects your actual skills (like your <b data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="221">UCMAS mental math</b> or your <b data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="247">Dairy Queen training</b>), just let me know and I can tweak the text to make it "Junior Developer" level so it feels more authentic for your Insta!</p><p data-path-to-node="14">How does the Vercel method sound to you?</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer complete gap"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" _nghost-ng-c1490227791="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1865031762-19 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c429900870="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-20 hide-action-bar ng-tns-c1865031762-19 ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-20"><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-20 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" _nghost-ng-c2375852602="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-20 ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2375852602="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Good response" aria-label="Good response" data-test-id="thumb-up-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-untheme