4="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1865031762-22"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-content ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-wrapper"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" data-test-id="model-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-24 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" xapautoid="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c3801849537-24"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c3801849537-24"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c3801849537-24 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" aria-controls="" aria-expanded="false" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-content animated-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="status" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c3801849537-24"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-24 ng-star-inserted">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c3801849537-24"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c3801849537-24 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_b42f0121804567ef" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_b42f0121804567ef" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">That is totally okay! Forget all the GitHub and Vercel stuff I just said. That was too many steps and too many different websites.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Let’s do the absolute easiest, <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="31">one-website method</b>. No downloading, no terminals, just pure copy and paste.</p><p data-path-to-node="2">Here is the exact 3-step cheat code to get your link right now:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="3">Step 1: Open Your Workspace</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="4"><li><p data-path-to-node="4,0,0">Go to a website called <b data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="23"><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c872387312="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c872387312="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c601438958="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_b42f0121804567ef&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_67c6746192d93ae0&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]]" href="https://codesandbox.io/" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahcKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQOQ">CodeSandbox.io</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,1,0">Click the <b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="10">"Sign Up"</b> or <b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="23">"Start for free"</b> button (you can just log in with Google).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,2,0">Once you are in, click the button that says <b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="44">"+ New Sandbox"</b> (or "+ Create").</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,3,0">Choose the option called <b data-path-to-node="4,3,0" data-index-in-node="25">"React"</b> or <b data-path-to-node="4,3,0" data-index-in-node="36">"React (Vite)"</b>.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="5">Step 2: Paste the Code</h3><p data-path-to-node="6">You will see a screen with files on the left, code in the middle, and a mini-browser on the right.</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="7"><li><p data-path-to-node="7,0,0">On the left side, click on <code data-path-to-node="7,0,0" data-index-in-node="27">App.jsx</code> (or <code data-path-to-node="7,0,0" data-index-in-node="39">App.js</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="7,1,0">Delete everything inside it, and <b data-path-to-node="7,1,0" data-index-in-node="33">paste</b> the <code data-path-to-node="7,1,0" data-index-in-node="43">App.jsx</code> code I gave you earlier.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="7,2,0">Click on <code data-path-to-node="7,2,0" data-index-in-node="9">index.css</code> (or <code data-path-to-node="7,2,0" data-index-in-node="23">styles.css</code>), delete everything, and <b data-path-to-node="7,2,0" data-index-in-node="59">paste</b> the CSS code.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="8">Step 3: Copy Your Link!</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="9"><li><p data-path-to-node="9,0,0">Look at the right side of your screen (the mini-browser showing your website).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,1,0">At the top of that mini-browser, there is a web address (it will look something like <code data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="85">[https://xyz123.csb.app](https://xyz123.csb.app)</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Copy that link.</b></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,3,0">Open Instagram, go to Edit Profile, and paste that link into your bio!</p></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="10"><p data-path-to-node="11">Does this sound a bit easier to manage, or would you prefer I rewrite the whole portfolio into just one single simple text file so you only have to copy and paste <i data-path-to-node="11" data-index-in-node="163">once</i>?</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer complete has-thoughts gap"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" _nghost-ng-c1490227791="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1