auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" xapautoid="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c3801849537-87"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c3801849537-87"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c3801849537-87 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" aria-controls="" aria-expanded="false" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-content animated-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="status" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c3801849537-87"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-87 ng-star-inserted">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c3801849537-87"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c3801849537-87 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_8fc9b79876045bb3" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_8fc9b79876045bb3" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Perfect. You are in exactly the right spot. We are going to create 5 files right there on that page.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Here is the exact rhythm you will follow for every single file:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="2"><li><p data-path-to-node="2,0,0">Click the <b data-path-to-node="2,0,0" data-index-in-node="10">Add file</b> button (near the top left/middle).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="2,1,0">Click <b data-path-to-node="2,1,0" data-index-in-node="6">Create new file</b> from the dropdown menu.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="2,2,0">Type the exact <b data-path-to-node="2,2,0" data-index-in-node="15">File Name</b> I give you below into the "Name your file..." box.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="2,3,0">Paste the <b data-path-to-node="2,3,0" data-index-in-node="10">Code</b> into the big black box.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="2,4,0">Click the green <b data-path-to-node="2,4,0" data-index-in-node="16">Commit changes...</b> button at the top right, and then click <b data-path-to-node="2,4,0" data-index-in-node="74">Commit changes</b> again on the popup.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="3">Let's do it one by one.</p><hr data-path-to-node="4"><h3 data-path-to-node="5">File 1</h3><ul data-path-to-node="6"><li><p data-path-to-node="6,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="6,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Click:</b> Add file &gt; Create new file</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="6,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Type this Name:</b> <code data-path-to-node="6,1,0" data-index-in-node="16">package.json</code></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="6,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Paste this Code:</b></p></li></ul><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c2578185806="" class="ng-tns-c2578185806-107 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="code-block ng-tns-c2578185806-107 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_8fc9b79876045bb3&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_64a2aef414c4471b&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQkgE" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c2578185806-107 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="ng-tns-c2578185806-107">JSON</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="buttons ng-tns-c2578185806-107 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" aria-label="Download code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Download code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c2578185806-107 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered=""><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" role="img" fonticon="download" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="download"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-but