</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><ul data-path-to-node="28"><li><p data-path-to-node="28,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="28,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Click:</b> Commit changes (twice)</p></li></ul><hr data-path-to-node="29"><h3 data-path-to-node="30">Final Step: Go Live!</h3><p data-path-to-node="31">Once all 5 files are saved in your GitHub:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="32"><li><p data-path-to-node="32,0,0">Open a new tab and go to <b data-path-to-node="32,0,0" data-index-in-node="25"><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c872387312="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c872387312="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c601438958="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_8fc9b79876045bb3&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_64a2aef414c4471b&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" href="https://vercel.com/" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQlwE">Vercel.com</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="32,1,0">Click <b data-path-to-node="32,1,0" data-index-in-node="6">Log in</b> at the top right and select <b data-path-to-node="32,1,0" data-index-in-node="41">Continue with GitHub</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="32,2,0">Once logged in, click the big black <b data-path-to-node="32,2,0" data-index-in-node="36">Add New</b> button and select <b data-path-to-node="32,2,0" data-index-in-node="62">Project</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="32,3,0">You will see a list of your GitHub repositories. Click the <b data-path-to-node="32,3,0" data-index-in-node="59">Import</b> button next to your portfolio repo.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="32,4,0">Do not change any settings. Just click the blue <b data-path-to-node="32,4,0" data-index-in-node="48">Deploy</b> button.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="33">Watch the screen—in about 60 seconds, it will give you your final <code data-path-to-node="33" data-index-in-node="66">.vercel.app</code> link that you can slap right into your Instagram bio! Let me know when you see the confetti!</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer has-thoughts gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" _nghost-ng-c1490227791="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762=