n="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c1865031762-129 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1865031762-129"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-content ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-wrapper"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" data-test-id="model-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-131 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" xapautoid="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c3801849537-131"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c3801849537-131"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c3801849537-131 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" aria-controls="" aria-expanded="false" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-content animated-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="status" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c3801849537-131"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-131 ng-star-inserted">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c3801849537-131"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c3801849537-131 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_6e6561ac983297f1" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_6e6561ac983297f1" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Let's go! 🎉 You did it.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">You now have a live, ultra-modern, fully functioning developer portfolio running on a global server.</p><p data-path-to-node="2">Copy that <code data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="10">.vercel.app</code> link and drop it right into your Instagram bio!</p><h3 data-path-to-node="3">The Best Part About This Setup</h3><p data-path-to-node="4">Now that everything is connected, you never have to deal with Vercel again.</p><p data-path-to-node="5">Whenever you want to change a word on your website—whether you decide to swap out the "Master's Degree" text later on to highlight your UCMAS mental math achievements, or add your Dairy Queen management certifications to your skills—here is all you do:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="6"><li><p data-path-to-node="6,0,0">Open your <code data-path-to-node="6,0,0" data-index-in-node="10">sujal-portfolio</code> repository on <b data-path-to-node="6,0,0" data-index-in-node="40">GitHub</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,1,0">Click on the <code data-path-to-node="6,1,0" data-index-in-node="13">src</code> folder, then click on <code data-path-to-node="6,1,0" data-index-in-node="39">App.jsx</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,2,0">Click the little <b data-path-to-node="6,2,0" data-index-in-node="17">pencil icon</b> (✏️) at the top right of the code box to edit it.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,3,0">Change whatever text you want.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,4,0">Click <b data-path-to-node="6,4,0" data-index-in-node="6">Commit changes</b>.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="7"><b data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="0">Vercel is literally watching your GitHub.</b> The second you click commit, Vercel will automatically rebuild your website in the background. If you refresh your <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="157">.vercel.app</code> link 60 seconds later, your new changes will be live on the internet!</p><p data-path-to-node="8">How does the site look on your phone? Does it have that smooth, heavy cinematic feel you were looking for?</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c2730877997="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" jslog="268370;track:generic_click,impression"><!----><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" _nghost-ng-c4229933914="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" _nghost-ng-c1490227791="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1865031762-129 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c429900870="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-132 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-132"><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-132 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" _nghost-ng-c2375852602="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-132 ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2375852602="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Good response" aria-label="Good response" data-test-id="thumb-up-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_6e6561ac983297f1&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_a0855e5c3c099114&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2375852602="" role="img" fonticon="thumb_up" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-m google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="thumb_up"></mat-icon><!-