-><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1865031762-157"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-content ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-wrapper"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" data-test-id="model-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-159 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" xapautoid="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c3801849537-159"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c3801849537-159"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c3801849537-159 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" aria-controls="" aria-expanded="false" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-content animated-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="status" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c3801849537-159"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-159 ng-star-inserted">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c3801849537-159"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c3801849537-159 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_394453072d9d1bc8" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_394453072d9d1bc8" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Yes, exactly! <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="14">App.jsx</code> needs to go <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="34">inside</b> the <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="45">src</code> folder you just created.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Here is the absolute foolproof way to make sure it goes in the exact right spot:</p><p data-path-to-node="2">When you click <b data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="15">Add file</b> &gt; <b data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="26">Create new file</b>, look at the box where you type the name.
Just type this exactly:
<code data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="108">src/App.jsx</code></p><p data-path-to-node="3">By typing <code data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="10">src/</code> first, GitHub will automatically force it into that folder, no matter where you currently are on the page.</p><p data-path-to-node="4">Then just paste that long block of code for File 5, hit <b data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="56">Commit changes</b> (twice), and you are 100% finished with GitHub!</p><p data-path-to-node="5">Let me know when you have all 5 files saved, and we will do the final 60-second Vercel step!</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c2730877997="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" jslog="268370;track:generic_click,impression"><!----><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" _nghost-ng-c4229933914="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" _nghost-ng-c1490227791="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1865031762-157 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c429900870="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-160 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-160"><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c4