;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_1269)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_1262)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c1865031762-163 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1865031762-163"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-content ng-star-inserted" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="thoughts-wrapper"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" data-test-id="model-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-166 ng-star-inserted" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" xapautoid="" class="model-thoughts ng-tns-c3801849537-166"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header ng-tns-c3801849537-166"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" mat-button="" data-test-id="thoughts-header-button" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c3801849537-166 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" aria-controls="" aria-expanded="false" jslog="247951;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-content animated-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="status" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c3801849537-166"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-166 ng-star-inserted">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c3801849537-166"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c3801849537-166 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span><span class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text contains-extensions-response processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_c0fd5f12e1792c80" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_c0fd5f12e1792c80" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Perfect! Yes, looking at your screenshot, that is exactly right. You are inside the folder, and both <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="101">App.jsx</code> and <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="113">main.jsx</code> are sitting perfectly right there together.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">If you click that little blue folder icon near the top left that says <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="70">..</code> (or click your repository name <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="104">sujal-portfolio</code> at the top), it will take you back out to your main page. As long as your <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="194">package.json</code>, <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="208">vite.config.js</code>, and <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="228">index.html</code> are sitting out on that main page, <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="274">you are 100% finished with GitHub!</b> 🎉</p><p data-path-to-node="2">Here is the final step to get your link right now:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="3">The Final Step: Get Your Link on Vercel</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="4"><li><p data-path-to-node="4,0,0">Open a new tab and go to <b data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="25"><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c872387312="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c872387312="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c601438958="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_c0fd5f12e1792c80&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_000153ee9fc9ce25&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" href="https://vercel.com/" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQywI">Vercel.com</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,1,0">Click <b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="6">Sign Up</b> (or Log In) at the top right, and choose <b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="55">Continue with GitHub</b>. (Authorize it if it asks for permission).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,2,0">Once you are logged in, look for a black button that says <b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="58">Add New...</b> and select <b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="80">Project</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,3,0">You will see a list of your GitHub repositories. Right next to <code data-path-to-node="4,3,0" data-index-in-node="63">sujal-portfolio</code>, click the <b data-path-to-node="4,3,0" data-index-in-node="90">Import</b> button.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,4,0">A setup screen will appear. <b data-path-to-node="4,4,0" data-index-in-node="28">Do not change any settings.</b> Just leave everything exactly as it is and click the blue <b data-path-to-node="4,4,0" data-index-in-node="114">Deploy</b> button.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="5">Now, just sit back and watch the screen. It takes about 60 seconds to build. When it finishes, the screen will shower you with confetti, and you will see your live <code data-path-to-node="5" data-index-in-node="164">.vercel.app</code> link right there on the screen to copy and paste into your Instagram bio!</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer contains-extensions-response gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserte