lass="thoughts-header-button-content animated-content"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="status" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c3801849537-172"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-172 ng-star-inserted">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c3801849537-172"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c3801849537-172 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted has-thoughts" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_645c4a0ce553faa4" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_645c4a0ce553faa4" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Editing your website is actually the easiest part of this entire process! Because Vercel is permanently linked to your GitHub, <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="127">you never have to log into Vercel again to make updates.</b> It works like magic: the second you save a change on GitHub, Vercel detects it and automatically updates your live website in the background.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Here is the exact step-by-step to make an edit whenever you want:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="2">How to Edit Your Site</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="3"><li><p data-path-to-node="3,0,0">Go to your <b data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="11">GitHub</b> account and open your <code data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="40">sujal-portfolio</code> repository.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,1,0">Click on the <b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="13"><code data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="13">src</code></b> folder, and then click on <b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="43"><code data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="43">App.jsx</code></b> (this is where all your text, skills, and about sections live).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,2,0">Look at the top right of the code box and click the little <b data-path-to-node="3,2,0" data-index-in-node="59">pencil icon (✏️)</b>. This puts you in edit mode.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,3,0">Scroll down through the code and change whatever text you want!</p><ul data-path-to-node="3,3,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="3,3,1,0,0"><i data-path-to-node="3,3,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">For example: You can scroll down to the "About Me" section, delete the part about the "Master's Degree in London," and type in your actual impressive achievements—like your UCMAS mental math levels or your Dairy Queen management training.</i></p></li></ul></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,4,0">Once you finish typing your changes, click the green <b data-path-to-node="3,4,0" data-index-in-node="53">Commit changes...</b> button at the top right, and then click <b data-path-to-node="3,4,0" data-index-in-node="111">Commit changes</b> again.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="4">What Happens Next?</h3><p data-path-to-node="5">That's it! Just close the tab. Wait about 60 seconds, go to your Instagram bio, click your <code data-path-to-node="5" data-index-in-node="91">.vercel.app</code> link, and your new changes will be live on the internet for everyone to see.</p><p data-path-to-node="6">Did you get your confetti screen on Vercel yet?</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c2730877997="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" jslog="268370;track:generic_click,impression"><!----><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" _nghost-ng-c4229933914="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" _nghost-ng-c1490227791="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1865031762-170 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c429900870="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-173 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-173"><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-173 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" _nghost-ng-c2375852602="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-173 ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2375852602="" mat-i