-c3801849537="" role="status" class="thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c3801849537-185"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="ng-tns-c3801849537-185 ng-star-inserted">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" class="thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c3801849537-185"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3801849537="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c3801849537-185 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts contains-extensions-response processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c3891909000="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3891909000="" _nghost-ng-c4035594071="" id="message-content-id-r_54c660e4f31f92dc" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4035594071="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_54c660e4f31f92dc" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Certainly. Let's make this portfolio as bold, interactive, and premium as possible by following the reference video's design and making your specific text edits.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">This will require a full rewrite of the main <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="45">App.jsx</code> file to replicate the cinematic full-screen video background, the powerful new hero typography, the custom cursor interaction, and the overall industrial-luxury feel of that video.</p><p data-path-to-node="2">Before we start the code, for the maximum effect, you will need a moody, low-light, cinematic video of yourself (in hoodie or smart casual) that can run as a seamless black-and-white background loop. Name it <code data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="208">cinematic-sujal.mp4</code> and place it on GitHub so Vercel can find it. If you don't have one, I will provide a placeholder.</p><p data-path-to-node="3">Here is the precise step-by-step for the edits.</p><hr data-path-to-node="4"><h3 data-path-to-node="5">Step 1: Update your GitHub <code data-path-to-node="5" data-index-in-node="27">index.html</code> file</h3><p data-path-to-node="6"><i data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="0">(This ensures your custom mouse cursor is visible and and removes default focus rings)</i></p><p data-path-to-node="7">Click on <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="9">index.html</code> on GitHub, click the pencil icon, and <b data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="58">replace</b> the <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="70">&lt;style&gt;</code> block with this one:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c2578185806="" class="ng-tns-c2578185806-195 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="code-block ng-tns-c2578185806-195 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_54c660e4f31f92dc&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_9fcc9e3cf4bb4a9a&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwilrsT8qbKUAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ5AM" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c2578185806-195 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="ng-tns-c2578185806-195">HTML</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" class="buttons ng-tns-c2578185806-195 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" aria-label="Download code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Download code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c2578185806-195 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered=""><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" role="img" fonticon="download" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="download"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" aria-label="Copy code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copy code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c2578185806-195 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_54c660e4f31f92dc&quot;,&quot;c_7d3130016a1c4b56&quot;,null,&quot;rc_9fcc9e3cf4bb4a9a&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2578185806="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon