 class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-user-query-label"> You said </span><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> listen first i dont want that pcicture insted set this like crete in perfect cinemetic way as it apper and ,,,Create a FULL cinematic premium developer portfolio website for “Sujal Patel” with ultra modern animations and exact high-end dark luxury aesthetic similar to award-winning portfolios on Awwwards. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> IMPORTANT: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> This should NOT look like a basic portfolio template. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> It must feel premium, futuristic, cinematic, smooth, interactive, luxury, intelligent, and visually powerful. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> STYLE &amp; THEME: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> * Dark black background (#050505) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> * Orange glow accent (#ff6a00) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> * White typography <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c412759700="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> * Cinematic lightin