                    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span>I am an ambitious international student, bridging my roots in India to the tech landscape of London. Beyond the code, I am a disciplined reader of psychology and self-growth literature.<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span>
                    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span>This perspective allows me to remain exceptionally calm under pressure. Whether debugging complex machine learning algorithms or deploying full-stack architectures, I adapt and build with precision.<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span>
