</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h3 data-path-to-node="10">What makes this code an absolute powerhouse:</h3><ul data-path-to-node="11"><li><p data-path-to-node="11,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">The <code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="4">&lt;TiltCard&gt;</code> System:</b> I created a custom physics wrapper. When your cursor enters any section (About, Skills, Stats), the cards actually calculate the X and Y math of your mouse and tilt toward it in 3D space (<code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="211">perspective: 1200</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Cinematic Audio Engine:</b> The <code data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="28">&lt;audio&gt;</code> tag is built in with a <code data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="59">useRef</code> hook. When you click "Sound On" in the top right, it smoothly initiates an ambient cinematic track.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Photographic Integration:</b> Your image (<code data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="38">heroImg</code>) is placed directly into the Hero background. I added <code data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="100">mix-blend-screen</code> and grayscale CSS filters so your blue suit fades perfectly into the dark orange luxury background, and when a user hovers over it, the color briefly returns!</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node="12">Upload the image, commit this new code to <code data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="42">App.jsx</code>, and watch Vercel update it in 60 seconds.</p><p data-path-to-node="13">Does this achieve that ultra-premium, interactive feeling you were going for?</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="response-footer contains-extensions-response gap has-thoughts complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><overview-carousel _nghost-ng-c2730877997="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" jslog="268370;track:generic_click,impression"><!----><!----><sources-sidebar-button _ngcontent-ng-c2730877997="" _nghost-ng-c4229933914="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-sidebar-button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></overview-carousel><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" _nghost-ng-c1490227791="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1865031762="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1865031762-197 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3655342764="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c429900870="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-203 ng-star-inserted" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-203"><div _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c429900870-203 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c429900870="" _nghost-ng-c2375852602="" class="ng-tns-c429900870-203 ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2375852602="" mat-icon-button="" mattool